PROTOCOL
------------------------------------------------------------------------

RavenTag implements the RTP-1 protocol (RavenTag Protocol v1),
an open standard for linking NTAG 424 DNA NFC chips to Ravencoin
blockchain assets. Protocol specification:
    https://github.com/ALENOC/RavenTag/blob/master/docs/protocol.md

